            <div class="well well-small">
              <h4>
		At this platform's core is the concept of a campaign, which is essentially a call to action. A sample campaign could be titled ‘stand up against bullying’, ‘make a terminally sick child’s day’, ‘feed a homeless person’, 'help victims of hurricane X' etc. A campaign could also be something a simple as a call to be more courteous in traffic. It is up to users to keep a campaign active by posting responses in the form of videos, images, stories and links. When you pledge a campaign you make a personal commitment to do whatever is at the core of said campaign. Our inaugural campaign is the '26 Acts of Kindness' campaign that NBC's Ann Curry launched via Twitter a month ago in honor of the 26 lives that were lost in Sandy Hook Elementary School on December 14th 2012.   
	      </h4>
